net.zer0bandwidth.android.lib.database

Interface SQLitePortal.ConnectionListener

  • Enclosing class:
    SQLitePortal

    public static interface SQLitePortal.ConnectionListener
    Classes interested in immediately reacting to a database's connection status may implement this interface to catch the event. Usually, connection times are fast enough that this is not necessary, and the database under the SQLitePortal may be used immediately.
    Since:
    zer0bandwidth-net/android 0.1.2 (#24)
